text: Two ATMs, on thr ground floor (no need enter the building) supporting cash deposit service, which is very convenient (the machine takes cash from $10). It is the neareast atm from nus that supports cash deposit.

They have replaced the 2 counters to a Video Teller Machine and only for Non Cash Services. While Card Services, Token Services and Account Updates are 24 hour services, other non cash services are available from 8:30am to 12am.
Currently they have staff stationed between 9am to 5pm to assist those who need help using the Video Teller Machine.
Do check out one of my uploaded photos for their operating hours and different services you can use via the Video Teller Machine.
A place that makes people happy and worried.
